replies.body:
Try triforce, steraks, sunfire, spiritvisage, Randulins, Mercurytreads on a few tank top laners like sion, poppy, ect... It's actually really good atm. If you can survive till you get triforce try blitzcrank top as well since he's really weak early but lategame full ad bruiser blitz is sooo strong.
Top lane {{champion:53}} 
{{item:3078}} {{item:3053}} {{item:3110}} {{item:3068}} {{item:3156}} {{item:3111}} 

People don't think he does damage but if you grab someone even remotely squishy you burst them with w atk speed and e doubling your base ad on top of really high base ad. If you weave your abilities right for the triforce procs you can do sooo much damage and the triple shield if you get caught out plus the insane lifesteal you get during it's duration when you fall on low hp makes you an exceptional duelist. Not to mention you can't kite this bruiser since you have the best grab in the game, an aoe silence and some decent base magic damage on your abilities.

On top of just being a blitzcrank, so I mean if you grab the right guy during a teamfight, you win the teamfight.
